synonym(3): kidney-specific Na-K-Cl symporter
synonym(4): Na-K-2Cl cotransporter
synonym(5): NKCC2
synonym(6): S12A1_HUMAN
synonym(7): solute carrier family 12 (sodium/potassium/chloride transporter), member 1
synonym(8): solute carrier family 12 (sodium/potassium/chloride transporters), member 1
